---
/* Hero section - full viewport with dark background and grid overlay */
---

<section class="min-h-screen flex items-center bg-brand-800 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Grid pattern overlay -->
  <div class="hero-grid absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- Radial gradient overlay -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(37,99,235,0.10), transparent 70%);"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 pt-32 pb-20">
    <p class="fade-in-up uppercase text-sm tracking-widest font-semibold text-amber-500 mb-4">
      Inteligencia de Mercados
    </p>

    <h1 class="fade-in-up text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      Convertimos datos en<br />estrategia comercial
    </h1>

    <p class="fade-in-up text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mb-10">
      Somos tu socio estratégico para construir áreas comerciales
      escalables, con el respaldo de inteligencia artificial para ganar
      velocidad y precisión. +10 años transformando empresas B2B y B2C
      en Argentina.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA buttons -->
    <div class="fade-in-up flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-0">
      <a
        href="#contacto"
        class="bg-amber-500 text-brand-800 font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-amber-400 transition-colors text-lg"
      >
        Agendá una consulta gratuita
      </a>
      <a
        href="#servicios"
        class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors text-lg"
      >
        Conocé nuestros servicios
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats bar -->
    <div class="fade-in-up flex flex-wrap items-center mt-16">
      <div class="pr-8 py-2">
        <span class="block text-2xl font-bold text-white">10+ años</span>
        <span class="block text-sm text-slate-400">de experiencia</span>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l border-brand-600 px-8 py-2">
        <span class="block text-2xl font-bold text-white">200+ empresas</span>
        <span class="block text-sm text-slate-400">transformadas</span>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l border-brand-600 px-8 py-2">
        <span class="block text-2xl font-bold text-white">B2B & B2C</span>
        <span class="block text-sm text-slate-400">cobertura integral</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
